<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Miky - OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FAE3C6; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width:600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #A67B5B; 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff; 
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: #5D4037; 
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #FAE3C6; 
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff; 
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFDDC1; 
            margin: 20px 0 5px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
 
        .footer {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #a3927d; 
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{title}}</h1>
        </div>
        <p>Hello, <strong>{{username}}</strong></p>
        <p>{{message}}</p>
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, just ignore this email.</p> 
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
